00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.744
Menu set measures are similarly
grouped as shown here.

00:00:04.744 --> 00:00:08.488
As with core measures,
you should easily be able to see a close

00:00:08.488 --> 00:00:12.520
alignment with the coordinated
management of chronic diseases,

00:00:12.520 --> 00:00:17.272
along with other key priorities, such
as ensuring privacy and security, and

00:00:17.272 --> 00:00:19.727
improve population and public health.

00:00:19.727 --> 00:00:24.378
The three mandatory clinical quality
measures are screening for weight,

00:00:24.378 --> 00:00:27.479
screening for and
diagnosing hypertension, and

00:00:27.479 --> 00:00:30.303
preventing care and
screening for smoking.

00:00:30.303 --> 00:00:33.210
All closely related to chronic disease.

